name: NAPD 1
notes: Chron uses top, St. Helens "Y" Ash (3400 yrs B.P.), and one C14 date. C14 dates BGS-627 and BGS-629 were considered contaminated with old carbon and not used. BGS-628 (103cm depth and 6cm thick) was not used as "could not calculate" a date.
